				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Why use something like blipbuf? Because otherwise the sound has a scratchy quality (due to aliasing) which pollutes the crystal-clear sound of the NES. This was evident in the recording you posted. I just wanted to bring it to your attention.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

						<table width="100%" cellspacing="0">
						<tr valign="middle">
